Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我鼓起勇气回头望去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正巧亚豆也转过头来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这0.1秒就像过了10秒钟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回过神来  焦急地向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  两三秒后我再次回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在远处的亚豆也再次回过头来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和亚豆的频率似乎完全吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:10.90,title,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天与分镜稿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,频率？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能亚豆望了你十次  只有两次碰巧对上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那种感觉还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解不能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我当傻瓜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我是羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到亚豆是在小六的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们读明小  亚豆是读明二小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学校间进行的游泳比赛的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和坐在对面加油的亚豆一直四目相望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候两人都没有觉得害羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  在中学开学典礼的时候再次相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时因为距离很近  我们两个都很快就把脸转了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  小学的时候就已经意识到对方的存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经互相喜欢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底  现在想想也觉得没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论频率有多么吻合  不交换手机邮件地址的话就没法联络哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手机邮件地址在毕业的时候再交换就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要专心于漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先看这五页
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在最高回忆期间我也在画嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两个地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们居住的地球不过是真实地球的复制品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人类也不过是住在真实地球上的人类的复制品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我们是真实人类所制造出来的实验材料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用来观察处于同样的环境中的自己的分身们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以此来创造更好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  在真实的地球上没有战争也没有气候变暖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是我们带来的研究成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋犯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？果然还是不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要画出分镜稿  难度实在太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很纠结  也不知道要怎么分格  画也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个故事是从哪抄袭来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有抄袭  有点相似的地方也没有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种故事  谁都能想到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是谁都能想到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我就想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说来  这个设定我很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这之后就只是真实地球的人类和这边的人类战斗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为能够预见才感兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不就可以尽情战斗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说  有比这个更有趣的体裁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我曾经也想过热血运动题材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫「墨镜投手」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个可以投出超速球并且立志成为职棒投手的小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被平直球击中而失明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十年后  职棒的投手板上突然出现了一名戴墨镜的投手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够以每秒180公里的速度投出高低内外角的各种球路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实现了完胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上  据说那名少年并没有放弃梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和父亲一起暗地里进行了十年特训
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.33,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}还没完呢 墨镜小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.57,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛看不见的事暴露之后  也与棒球协会发生过纠纷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他还是想和能够击中他的球的对手们继续战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然秋犯很有才能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种设定一般无法进展到这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？你真的觉得我有才能？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一般人会觉得这故事很荒唐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  其实我每天都在一个劲地想故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我有点自信过头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得到最高的认同后  让我有自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会努力  要画出不会输给秋犯的故事的画来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  要做哪一篇？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「两个地球」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「墨镜投手」感觉比较倾向连载
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有理想的页数吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新人赏似乎规定是31页或者是45页
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那样也行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先不要在意页数  尽力画出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为序章已经在我脑海中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  就算进度很快  但要是故事没趣的话也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最高？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？啊  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高木  过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在叫你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  她走过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明叫了你  居然无视我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好像很生气的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无视无视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高木  我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走啦  坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我被美保骂了  她问我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「为什么高木君会知道我的梦想  你告诉他了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又没什么关系  我只是去向她本人确认而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我跟他说了  我朋友真城君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了  美保是很害羞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你不要跟别人说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  不会再告诉别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  请你转告她说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她这么害羞的人怎么当得成声优
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话我才说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我不会再告诉别人了  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  你被美保拒绝了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？不要开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是跟美保说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  我只是想确认那是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且亚豆有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道  不过一般都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟她也是中学三年级的女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是啊  不过美保不会说这方面的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  那你为什么要向我调查美保的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  这是因为…我之前想和见吉说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让…让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  等等  见吉…同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你玩得过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你说是开玩笑的话  她肯定不是哭就是发飙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙啊  好像据说有参加过空手道还是合气道的全国比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我觉得她本来就喜欢秋犯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把好朋友的秘密都告诉你了  对你相当有好感了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且说考虑一下什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的话是不会这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,见吉她人也不坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？不坏？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亚豆的好朋友肯定都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  香耶  突然说要找我谈话的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高木向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得高木怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…学习成绩也很好  长得又高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  和我完全不搭调嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事  香耶很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高木君也是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,香耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我们班的人都在传
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说高木肯定和岩濑在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  岩濑同学会让男生觉得高不可攀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人都是笨蛋  是这种感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不到那种地步啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美保喜欢的人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.47,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}所以说  嗯？嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  香耶  不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.09,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那就快点说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美保肯定也和岩濑一样让男生觉得高不可攀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有看到过你跟男生讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这点来说就是高傲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,香耶  我只是因为害羞而不敢和男生讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我比香耶更喜欢男孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是因为我没有哥哥弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会很在意  一下子就会脸红所以没法好好说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美保有时候会用老师的口气说话  真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你这么认真地跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就明白你不是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,香耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回复高木君的时候要一个人去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说什么一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高木他们回来了  怎…怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是频率吻合了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才只是见吉回头了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么「只是」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,画了这么多次都不满意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明马上就要暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强  我也还没有画出原稿的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟的情况  我画前面的时候你把后面做出来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第六名？不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在班级第六啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟秋犯说的一样  考试题都是那个模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,频…频率
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然爸爸说没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过假期一直窝在工作室里妈妈我可是不同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也要回来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  最高  也让我住下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是可以  你家父母不会说你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,川口太郎老师就是喝着那个努力画画的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也这样努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋犯原来还这么重形式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再来次  暑假中要完成原稿！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒  我的分镜稿变成漫画了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是分镜稿  只是我修改了分格和构图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉上了墨线之后会变成很不错的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离完成还远呢  下面要先画草稿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勾线不是马上就能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到那一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要继续提升画技到一定水平之后再勾线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最高  虽说漫画没有界限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你的理想高过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起来已经很好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  最高就按照自己想做的去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会做出让自己满意的分镜稿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我不会干涉你的分镜稿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋犯也不干涉我的画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最高  睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能这么快就睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是  用脑过度反倒睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续看漫画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真会利用时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有什么有趣的漫画吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  果然还是龙珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你本来就喜欢的漫画嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以说是我的坚持或者说是原点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你以前玩过龙珠游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩过玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,融合  哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋犯  「合」的时机慢了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的「合」可是很完美的  是你的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  说「合」的时候要喊成「合！」这样才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的并不是真正的「合」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说我的「酱」是冒牌货？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「酱」是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最高你也起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要尝试勾线了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假也过了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我还是不满意我画画时的手感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过再不开始的话就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会催你快点写分镜稿什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋犯就坚持做到让自己满意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  中章结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了  休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  最高也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个用白色墨水能修白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出去走走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}本周排名第一的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:38.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}七月发行的大碟已经破百万的koogy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐  这首曲子很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是koogy吧  新大碟里面的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去夏季巡回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  暑假得尽情玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去继续工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最高？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经做到这一步了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去趟便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,买东西的话我去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为接下来的原稿我可帮不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  联系亚豆的话说不定会过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说着「主人  餐点准备好了」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望最高能恢复精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道亚豆不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  我想拿本书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊  没去附近的便利店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  不是平常的那家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  帮我买了JUMC回来啊  谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻英二…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,英二很厉害  不只是画  故事也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说输的话就是输在画上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最…最高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想输  但是没想到他的故事都这么精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么我可以帮忙的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋犯一个人完成了分镜稿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想一个人完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  修白完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最高  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干涉分镜稿  秋犯不干涉画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  我是想跟你一起迎接完成的那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能贴网点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把地球军的裤子全部用这个贴上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样不要停下一直做到完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,画很好  不过我的故事就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故事很好  不过我的画就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最高
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  做这种事你不害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  最高
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们马上就打电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在电话本里应该有号码吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这台电话打的话会不会让人觉得川口太郎诈尸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人会记得啦  不然就拿手机打
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就说「我有原稿想自荐」什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我打了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  这里是少年JUMC编辑部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们带着第一次完成的漫画来到了JUMC编辑部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.71,0:24:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,见到的编辑是好是坏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.13,0:24:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓起干劲上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  糖与鞭子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.10,0:24:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想是甜的  现实却很苦

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:49.83,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,在蓝天下交错乱飞的Blue  Bird
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.02,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以看见那只青鸟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.06,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,总是看不到的幸福  Color  却一直感受着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:07.51,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}Your love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:18.37,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,牵挂重重  填满春日的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:22.61,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,抬头仰望  又俯首下看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:27.37,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,再次仰起脸时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:35.67,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,决定在这条街上找到梦想的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:44.01,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}将无法抹去的事铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.26,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,Your love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:51.66,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,在蓝天下交错乱飞的Blue Bird
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:55.77,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以看见那只青鸟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:02:03.21,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,总是看不到的幸福  Color  却一直感受着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.58,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,Your love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:50.30,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在更好的现实面前支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:56.47,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,被打垮的自己  也要重拾信心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:23:01.22,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,探寻过无数次结局也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:07.57,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都要拍拍自己的背
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:12.49,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,苦恼着继续前进的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:17.37,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那种迷茫 需要斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:18.54,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,总是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:23.66,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,描绘出未来的轮廓  笔直的尺子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:29.34,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,是在无数个昨日的勇气中产生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:34.42,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,不同于所想所绘  越过高高的墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:40.47,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着消失点的方向前进着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:46.63,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:52.64,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是别人正是自己的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:24:00.24,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,将自己微小的梦想  全部燃尽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:04.43,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,用光芒劈开黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.43,0:24:08.48,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,粉碎的墙壁对面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.48,0:24:14.07,OPC2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}能看见属于自己的天空
